Arthur Schopenhauer

Arthur ; 21 1860) was German philosopher. work "The Will and in he the a metaphysical will. Building the Schopenhauer atheistic and ethical that rejected the contemporaneous ideas idealism. was among Western share tenets Eastern as asceticism and notion world-as-appearance. His has been described as of pessimism.

Though substantial attention during lifetime, has had a posthumous various including and writing on aesthetics, and psychology influenced and and centuries. Those cited his influence philosophers Wittgenstein, and Anthony Ludovici, Einstein, Freud and Carl and as Leo Thomas Assis, Jorge Borges, and Samuel

